# Docker build context excludes — keep the image lean + deterministic.
**/node_modules
**/target
.git
.github
data/
*.log
C4-Documentation/
# the operator-ui dist is rebuilt inside the image (build stage); never ship the host's copy
apps/operator-ui/dist/
# the untracked root lockfile is not used by the image (root deps resolve fresh; see ci.md)
package-lock.json
